  "abstract": "This ninth annual report covers the 1982 calendar year. It includes work done at ICRISAT Center near Hyderabad, India, at research stations on the campuses of agricultural universitties in different climatic regions of India, and at national and international research facilities in the 10 countries of Africa, Latin America, and West Asia where ICRISAT scientists are posted.",
